Garnished with brown and white chocolate flakes, along with rich Colombian coffee powder sprinkled at the sides, this cake justifies - they aren't just meant to celebrate occasions but life as well!

Title: Nutty Coffee Secret
Introducing: An overwhelming blend of chocolate cake and espresso-infused butter cream icing along with crunchy walnut.
Description: This is going to spellbind the coffee lovers with the unforgettable magical taste of the Classic Coffee Walnut. Prepared with three layers of Chocolate Cake and generous icing of intensely whipped Coffee in fresh cream and butter that gives an irresistible aroma of espresso, along with sprinkled crunchy walnuts is something we all adore!

Title: Exotic Affair
Introducing: Stay hooked to deliciousness of this heart-shaped Chocolate cake that'll add charm to your fete!
Description: A single bite of this cake is going to bind you with its captivating taste. Perfect for all occasions like Birthdays, Anniversaries, Valentine's etc, this gorgeously rich heart shaped chocolate cake graced with hand crafted rose fondant is the ultimate delight to savour! We bet this one is going to add undying memories to your occasion.

Title: Sunshine Poise
Introducing: Satiate your summertime desires with this delicious mango cake that'll leave you with a sweet craving.
Description:
"Do not forget to add this mango cake in your list of 'must-haves' this summer. The richly whipped moist cheese cake topped with mango pulp and fresh mango slices has everything to qualify as your ""Favourite Summer Cake."" Well, not just this, be all set to be served this delicacy all year through and delight yourself!
Note: The mango slices used for garnishing depends on availability of the fruit"

Title: Sun-kissed Joys
Introducing: This mushy cake baked with pineapple & cherries is a wholesome treat to surprise you with a unique flavor
Description: Don't feel surprised by this sheer beauty seared fantastically to add a uniquely delicious taste to the cake. Moist cake topped with pineapple and maraschino cherries baked wholesomely is a new arrival in the town to turn all your celebrations into a happy one.

Title: Irish Delight
Introducing: Time for some Irish Shots! Savour the scrumptious taste of magnificently rich and intensely flavoured Irish cake!
Description: The heavenly flavoured Irish delight with triple layered rich cream cake is a heavenly dessert that no one would refuse to go along with! Loaded with intensely whipped rich Irish cream and excellently adorned with chocolate glaze, this cake is just perfect for office and family gatherings!
